<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>DigitalKrishi</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  body { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; margin:0;color: black; padding:0; }
  header { background: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 1rem 2rem; display:flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items:center; }
  header nav a { color:white; margin-left:1rem; text-decoration:none; font-weight:bold; }
  .hero { background: url('farm-hero.jpg') center/cover no-repeat; height:90vh; display:flex; flex-direction:column; justify-content:center; align-items:center; color:white; text-align:center; }
  .hero h1 { font-size:3rem; margin-bottom:1rem; color: black;}
  .hero p { font-size:1.5rem; margin-bottom:2rem; color: black; }
  .hero button { background:#FFD700; color:#333; padding:1rem 2rem; font-size:1rem; border:none; border-radius:5px; cursor:pointer; font-weight:bold; }
  .features { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr)); gap:2rem; padding:3rem; text-align:center; }
  .feature-card { background:#f0f0f0; padding:2rem; border-radius:10px; }
  footer { background:#333; color:white; padding:2rem; text-align:center; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="logo"><h2>DigitalKrishi</h2></div>
  <nav>
    <a href="/features">Features</a>
    <a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
    <a href="/forum">Forum</a>
    <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <h1>Grow Smarter with DigitalKrishi</h1>
  <p>Real-time crop insights, weather updates, and soil monitoring to boost your farm productivity.</p>
  <button>Get Started</button>
</section>

<section class="features" id="features">
  <div class="feature-card">
    <a href="/moisture">Moisture Monitoring</a>
    <p>Keep track of soil moisture in real-time and get alerts for irrigation needs.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="feature-card">
    <a href="/weather">Weather-based Crop Suggestions</a>
    <p>Get crop recommendations based on current weather conditions in your area.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="feature-card">
    <a href="/marketprice">Market Prices</a>
    <p>Check real-time crop prices to plan your selling strategy effectively.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  &copy; 2025 DigitalKrishi | Helping Farmers Grow Smarter
</footer>

</body>
</html>
